OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fincreasing overnight and thickening
OL,7,Flater, but all parts likely staying
OL,8,Fdry. Winds also gradually
OL,9,Fstrengthening, and turning gusty by
OL,10,Fdawn. Likely staying frost free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA cloudy but dry start, but
OL,13,Fsome outbreaks of light rain possible
OL,14,Fby early afternoon. These turning more
OL,15,Fpersistent through the evening, with
OL,16,Fheavy rain arriving overnight. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
